    "description": "\"A Careless Word... a Needless Sinking\"",
    "justification": null,
    "gallery_text": "This poster comes from a series of posters with the text \u201cA Careless Word\u2026\u201d. The various endings, that followed, were directed specifically to naval and military personnel. The purpose of the campaign was to present the possible consequences if military personnel did not mind with whom, or where, they were discussing military tactics. \u201cA Careless Word\u2026A Needless Sinking\u201d is meant to show the repercussions of \u201cloose lips\u201d, so to speak, because one was never sure when the enemy was nearby, or who the enemy might be.",
    "label_text": "A Careless Word depicts a lifeboat loaded with distressed and wounded sailors pulling away from a burning ship. As viewers, we put ourselves in the boat with the sailors, seeing the devastation from their perspective.",
